latestIgtvVideos.title: RISE AGAIN
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Covid- 19 is here to stay. The world is working out on how to live with it. Are you doing the same? You may be exhausted, but this is not the time for it. This is the time to challenge ourselves, challenge to adapt the situation, and challenge to thrive in the new normal. 

I, Rahul Dev Shetty, am getting back to our New Normal with my mask and hygiene regimes, and urge every individual to not to settle back. This is the time for us to Rise again. Thank you JD institute of Fashion Technology for giving me this wonderful opportunity and bringing out the beautiful initiative to rise again in the new normal.
